rows.label: qst103613_msg0002
rows.name:
We've had notification from the
Invidian government that the
senator will be extradited.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0003
rows.name:
His son is being held safely
at a military installation.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0005
rows.name:
What kind of a parent puts
his child through that...

rows.label: qst103613_msg0006
rows.name:
I think he'll be all right
in the end, though.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0007
rows.name:
What? There are still
anti-imperialist agents at large?!

rows.label: qst103613_msg0009
rows.name:
Sorry, but I don't really
have any information that
would help you right now.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0010
rows.name:
It seems that we've
encountered an impasse.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0012
rows.name:
Our purpose in life is to defend
the Emperor and the Empire!

rows.label: qst103613_msg0013
rows.name:
If we continue our search, we're
sure to find something that leads
us to those scoundrels!

rows.label: qst103613_msg0014
rows.name:
You have a fire in your soul,
Wadatsumi. You wouldn't think
so to look at you.

rows.label: qst103613_msg0015
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Think ] Perhaps this is Rex's influence?

rows.label: qst103613_msg0016
rows.name: Everyone! Let's look for some clues!
